verbose_text: Previous pharmacodynamic and acute toxicity investigations of cbFeD have shown that it can enhance gastrointestinal peristalsis, improve tolerance to fatigue and hypoxia, and can promote the recovery of Hb, RBCs, IgG, and the immunosuppressive effect in hemorrhagic blood deficient mice.
